                 "transferred below maternal: %s — the hierarchy of selective, FcRn-mediated ",
                 "transplacental transfer, in which the best-transferred subclass is actively ",
                 "concentrated in the fetal circulation. The per-arm split is in Tables 7-8 and Figure A1; ",
                 "see also the per-analyte (Table 5), per-antigen (Table 6) breakdowns and the ",
                 "Interpretation section below."),
          n_mostly_inc, n_mostly_dec, n_mixed,
          if (length(inc_an_v)) paste(inc_an_v, collapse = ", ") else "none",
